com.jdbwc.core

Class WCStaticMetaData

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.jdbwc.core.WCStaticMetaData

  • public final class WCStaticMetaData
extends java.lang.Object
    A static metadata producer. Primarily for metadata about metadata.
    This class is database independent. Its results can be used with any of the JDBWC database implementations.
    Version:
    2010-04-30
    Author:
    Tim Gall
